** Outcome
Clarifying outcomes
View the project from beyond the completion date. A useful exercise is to write a future newspaper article reporting on the success of your project. Describe what happened, and what you achieved.
Envision Wild Success.
Write down the features, aspects and qualities you want to have in your successful project.
